
Introduction
------------

Narradar is a tool for automatic proving of termination of logic programs and narrowing.

author: Pepe Iborra
maintainer: pepeiborra@gmail.com
homepage: http://github.com/pepeiborra/narradar


Installation
------------

There is a hackage repository available to facilitate the installation of Narradar:

http://safe-tools.dsic.upv.es/~pepe/haskell

The hackage repository contains updated versions of all the dependencies.

